Question: The image on the left has a single jellyfish with many tiny brown spots on its top section

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many jellyfish are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the jellyfish have many tiny brown spots on its top section?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
